<Content>SAFE Taxi drivers I have been in your hotel from 11.-13.07.2004. Then we wanted to go to the Busstation south with an Volkwagen Taxi (my girlfriend has never been driven with an old Volkswagen).Your Hotelservice decided that we have to use your SAFE Taxis which will cost 120Pesos.At the Busstation your SAFE taxidriver charged us 140Pesos. I just had a hundred and a 50 Pesos note and the Tasxidriver told us that he is not able to change.After 5 minutes discussion with your SAFE taxidriver that we are not going to give him a tip on his not agreed Price he suddenly found coins in his taxidoor.This ist not the way we are making deals.I will never recommend a hotel to somebody if this is the understanding of service to guests you think you will never see then again.best regardsMussehlPS: 3 collegues of mine are waiting for my notes of the trip. They are going to mexice this year too. What do you think i will write about yor hotel? 
